Match Day 1 in the Premier League continues on Sunday. Newcomers Sheffield United host Crystal Palace in the first of two fixtures for the day. Leicester City travel to Chelsea in the second match. The Blues are looking to bounce back, after back-to-back losses against Manchester United and Liverpool. Sunday, August 18
